g stack:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>LangGraph</strong> — for agentic workflow orchestration (ReAct pattern)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Groq</strong> — LLM inference</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Tavily</strong> — web search tool</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Streamlit</strong> — frontend UI</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Current state of the project:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ Persistent <strong>SQLite-based conversation history</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✅ <strong>Chat with PDF</strong> (RAG use case using FAISS + HuggingFace embeddings)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">🔲 <strong>Third feature</strong> — extended tool calling (scoped but not yet implemented)</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">We had also discussed that you'd want to pick up the third feature from where the last session left off.</p>
