<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Re-evaluation</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">For a B.Tech student in placement season, the bar isn't "production SaaS." It's:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Does it show conceptual depth beyond tutorials?</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Can you defend every design decision?</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Does it differentiate you from 200 other candidates?</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">On that scale — <strong>8.2/10</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Here's why I revised up:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">LangGraph with persistent memory + RAG + tool calling in <strong>one unified project</strong> is rare at undergrad level. Most students submit three separate notebooks.</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">SQLite for conversation history shows you thought about <strong>state across sessions</strong>, not just within one chat.</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">FAISS + HuggingFace (not just OpenAI embeddings) shows you understand the embedding layer independently.</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Groq as the inference backend signals awareness of <strong>latency optimization</strong> — a real engineering concern.</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>How to push it to 9.5/10</strong></p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.6)] py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Area</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.6)] py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">What to add</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.6)] py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Impact</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Third feature</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Finish extended tool calling (calculator, code executor, or multi-tool chaining)</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Completes the story</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">UI</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Replace Streamlit with a minimal React frontend</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Signals full-stack awareness</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Observability</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Add LangSmith tracing</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Shows production mindset</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Evaluation</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Basic RAG eval (faithfulness + relevance scores)</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(--border-300)/0.3)] py-2 pr-4 align-top">Defensible in viva</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-[hsl(var(-