<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>This is significant for your resume/viva.</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">You can now say with full confidence:</p>
