<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Important:</strong> <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">chat_history</code> already has the current user message appended via <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">_persist()</code> before the graph call — so no need to append it again.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
