<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">In Basic Chatbot, <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">_persist("user", ...)</code> is called <strong>before</strong> building history:</p>
