<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Current honest state: 8.5/10</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Here's what's still missing for a true 10/10:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Critical gaps (high impact):</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>1. System Prompt missing in Basic Chatbot</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Right now the LLM has no identity. Add:</p>
